These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, old-henry, siglo, cain, blend
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, lacrosse, skiing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the cain-smoker##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | tiparillo | siglo | cain | blend  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skiing    | cycling | baseball  | swimming |

