 7. the person who likes coral is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
