 1. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of ambient##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the american##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 9. the german is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
