 1. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the person playing bridge is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of folk##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
