There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, british, italian, polish, thai
The people have 5 different hobbies: photography, dancing, reading, magic-tricks, fishing
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the thai##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the fan of pop is the british##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the polish is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

